If you have strong desire to look for challenges, development of creativity and personal growth, this is a good opportunity for you to develop your career in CLDW. We offer rewarding career opportunity and attractive package. For further information about us, please visit www.cldw.com.hk.

Main Job Duties:

Responsible for account servicing, project management from budgeting, Client & Contractor coordination, production implementation, on-site set-up and dismantle supervision;
